{
  "texts": [
    "However, if they fell outside this range, we utilized max-min normalization to rescale the intensity values to [0, 255].",
    "Finally, to meet the model's input requirements, all images were resized to a uniform size of 1024 × 1024 × 3.",
    "In the case of whole-slide pathology images, patches were extracted using a sliding window approach without overlaps.",
    "The patches located on boundaries were padded to this size with 0.",
    "As for 3D CT and MR images, each 2D slice was resized to 1024 × 1024, and the channel was repeated three times to maintain consistency."
  ]
}